 he should drop the key for the small chest on the table.<BR>Kiya<BR></FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtextureL.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">FRS</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">I was moving barrels and stuff around there like crazy until I realized that that 'strong table' in the room contained 3 items (keys).<BR>then I let the snake out just for fun, the cow is right.<P>After I found a way to convert the animals back, I converted the snake and he turns into an orc warlord! Big foe for such a small basement. You can always just repolymorph him with the spell...<BR>-FRS</FONT></TD></TR><TR background="http://www.larian.com/ubb/forumtexture.jpg"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Kudarat</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Thanks for the answer. im going to check if i didn't touch the table. Actually, ive been moving all the things in the room and i cant find anything but i cant remember if ive move the table.<P></FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
